configuration.name: preprocessScript
forceConfig.soqlQuery
configuration.value:
SELECT Id,
Name,
Type,
BillingStreet,
BillingCity,
BillingState,
BillingPostalCode,
BillingCountry,
ShippingStreet,
ShippingCity,
ShippingState,
ShippingPostalCode,
ShippingCountry,
Phone,
Fax
FROM Account
WHERE Id > '${OFFSET}'
ORDER BY Id
